Iyada oo la tixraacayo baahida xaaladaha isbitaalka ee COVID-19 ee wadamada EU/EEA iyo UK, xaaladaha qaabeynta ee isku xirnaanta awoodda daryeelka caafimaadka ayaa muujinaya in khatarta ah in > 90% ee kartida sariiraha daryeelka daran ay ka baxdo, sida lagu sheegay cusbooneysiinta lixaad ee Qiimaynta Khatarta Degdega ah ee ECDC ee COVID-19.
