Inta badan waxyaabaha ay ka kooban yihiin lama yaqaan ama lama garanayo, maadaama ay adagtahay in la soo saaro ama la hubiyo waxyaabahaas ama isku darkooda.
Waqtigan xaadirka ah, la'aanta daaweynta wax ku oolka ah ee COVID-19, TCM waxay noqotay mid ka mid ah daaweynta ugu muhiimsan ee loogu talagalay bukaannada qaba calaamadaha fudud ama dhexdhexaadka ah ama kuwa ka soo kabashada marxaladaha daran.
Tusaale ahaan, Shu Feng Jie Du iyo Lian Hua Qing Wen ayaa lagu ogaaday inay waxtar u leeyihiin daaweynta COVID-19.
Xanuunka ayaa ka muuqday gobollo badan oo Shiinaha ah oo isticmaalay TCM 87% bukaanada, kuwaas oo ay ka mid yihiin Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%) iyo Hunan (50%), halka gobolka Hubei, oo kaliya 30% bukaanada COVID-19 ay isticmaaleen TCM, uu ahaa midka ugu hooseeya (13%).
