Waxaa xiiso leh, in heerka hoos u dhaca astaamaha (mid fudud ilaa mid daran) uu si weyn uga hooseeyo kooxda WM+TCM marka loo eego kooxda WM oo keliya (7.4% vs. 46.2%), iyo heerka dhimashada ee kooxda WM+TCM marka loo eego kooxda WM oo keliya (8.8% vs. 39%).
