Hay'adaha caafimaadka ayaa soo saaray tilmaamo faahfaahsan oo ku saabsan is-karantiil ku habboon. Dowlado badan ayaa qasab ka dhigaya ama ku talinaya is-karantiil dhammaan dadka deggan aagagga ay saameynta ku yeelatay.
