Dadka la soo xiriiray qof qaba COVID-19 iyo kuwa dhawaan u safray wadamo ama gobollo ay ka jiraan faafitaan ballaaran ayaa lagula talinayaa inay is karantiimeeyaan 14 maalmood laga bilaabo waqtiga ugu dambeeya ee ay la xiriireen.
