Inkastoo siyaasadaha ka hortagga ugu wanaagsan ay yareeyeen baahida daryeelka caafimaadka ee 2/3 iyo dhimashada nus, haddana nidaamyada caafimaadka ayaa wali la burburiyaa iyadoo ay jiraan malaayiin dhimasho ah.
