ACE2 waxay ka hortageysaa shaqada enzyme-ka angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) iyadoo la yareynayo xaddiga angiotensin-II iyo kor u qaadista Ang ((1-7) taas oo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed daroogo oo rajo leh oo lagu daaweynayo cudurka wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u adeegtaa sidii meel ay ku galaan unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-ka.
Nooca aadanaha ee enzyme waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin-modifying enzyme 2 waa metallosome zinc-ka ku jira oo ku jira dusha sare ee endothelial iyo unugyada kale.
ACE2 wuxuu leeyahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal colectin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waa protein-ka hal-mar-mar-mar ee nooca I ee membrane-ka, kaas oo meesha uu ka shaqeeyo kaabayaasha uu ka muuqdo dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
ACE2 waxaa laga soo saaraa domain ka mid ah transmembrane by enzyme kale oo loo yaqaan sheddes, waxaana ka soo baxa borotiinka lagu milmi karo ee dhiigga iyo ugu dambeyntii kaadida.
ACE2 waxay ku jirtaa xubnaha badankood: ACE2 waxay ku xidhan tahay unugyada unugyada la xiriira alveolus nooca II ee sambabada, enterocytes-ka mindhicirka yar, unugyada badankood ee xididdada iyo unugyada xididdada ee unugyada iyo unugyada muruqyada ee xididdada.
