ACE waxay kala jajabisaa hormoonka angiotensin I oo loo yaqaan angiotensin II.
ACE2 waxay ka soo qaadaa angiotensin II amino acid-ka carboxyl-terminal ee phenylalanine (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) waxayna ku dheecaan angiotensin (1-7) oo ah vasodilator (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
