ACE2 oo ah borotiin transmembrane ah ayaa u adeega sida barta ugu weyn ee galaan-celceliska qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-yada, oo ay ka mid yihiin HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (viruska keena SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska keena COVID-19).
